Package: till
Version: 1.1.0-1
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: bash (>= 5), coreutils, mmdebstrap, proot
Maintainer: You <0foo.dev>
Description: Tiny rootless Debian env manager for per-project dev (mmdebstrap + proot)
 This tool bootstraps a minimal Debian rootfs per project using mmdebstrap
 (rootless) and enters it with proot (also rootless). The current working
 directory is bind-mounted inside by default, preserving your usual workflow.
 .
 Commands:
  - 'till build'  : create/update the rootfs under the project
  - 'till enter'  : proot into it (use --no-bind-pwd to disable PWD bind, --as-root for fake root)
